

#VarATTACHURL
---+++ ATTACHURL -- full URL for attachments in the current topic
   * Syntax: =%<nop>ATTACHURL%=
   * Expands to: =%ATTACHURL%=
   * Example: If you attach a file you can refer to it as =%<nop>ATTACHURL%/image.gif=
   * Related: [[%IF{"'%INCLUDINGTOPIC%'='Macros'" then="#"}%VarATTACHURLPATH][ATTACHURLPATH]], [[%IF{"'%INCLUDINGTOPIC%'='Macros'" then="#"}%VarPUBURL][PUBURL]], [[%IF{"'%INCLUDINGTOPIC%'='Macros'" then="#"}%VarPUBURLPATH][PUBURLPATH]], [[%IF{"'%INCLUDINGTOPIC%'='Macros'" then="#"}%VarSCRIPTURL][SCRIPTURL]], [[%IF{"'%INCLUDINGTOPIC%'='Macros'" then="#"}%VarSCRIPTURL][SCRIPTURLPATH]], FileAttachments

